title: How To | How To Contour
description:
Bronzer is a great way to brighten and contour in a natural and simple way. 

Step 1: Start at your cheekbones and brush bronzer back towards your hairline.   

Step 2: Apply bronzer to temples & hairline.

Step 3: Apply bronzer along jawline.

Now you’re ready for any occasion. Follow our ‘How To’ series for more everyday makeup tips!

transcripts: Bronzer is a great way to brighten and contour the face in the most natural way.  Start on the front of your cheekbones and work your bronzer back with your brush towards your hairline. This will create the illusion of more lifted and rounded cheekbone. For step 2 to balance out the look, you're going to apply bronzer to your temples and hairline. And lastly to finish up your contour, you're going to work your bronzer along your jawline and you're ready for any occasion.
